sentences.en: A valid account name including a domain qualifier is required.
sentences.cn: 必须填写包含域限定符的有效帐户名称.

sentences.en: Alias'{ 0 }'is standard alias, it's qualifier can not be changed.
sentences.cn: 别名 “ {0}”是标准别名, 不能更改它的限定符.

sentences.en: Cech said: We had to disguise my injury right before the qualifier against Armenia.
sentences.cn: 门神说: 在预选赛上,面对亚美尼亚之前,我必须要隐瞒自己的伤情.

sentences.en: Concentrating switching function qualifier. Right - click for expanding switching function.
sentences.cn: 集中开关功能限定符. 右击指定扩展开关功能.

sentences.en: Kenya's Robert Kibe was the fastest qualifier for the 800 metres final.
sentences.cn: 肯尼亚的罗伯特·基布是800米决赛入围者中速度最快的选手.

sentences.en: Last week Wales lost 5-1 to Romania in a World Cup qualifier.
sentences.cn: 在上周的世界杯预选赛中，威尔士队1比5负于罗马尼亚队。

sentences.en: Party Name, Qualifier and Value are mandatory fields.
sentences.cn: 参与方名称 、 限定符和值均是必需字段.

sentences.en: Please fill all fields: Party Name, Qualifier and Value.
sentences.cn: 请填写所有字段: 参与方名称 、 限定符和值.

sentences.en: Qualifier of a namespace must be unique in a schema file.
sentences.cn: 命名空间的限定符在架构文件中必须是唯一的.

sentences.en: Scotland were ahead in their European championship qualifier in Iceland.
sentences.cn: 苏格兰队在冰岛举行的欧洲杯预选赛中处于领先位置。

sentences.en: Switching function qualifier. Concentrating or expanding can be specified.
sentences.cn: 开关功能限定符. 可指定集中或扩展.

sentences.en: The tournament was won by a late qualifier.
sentences.cn: 锦标赛冠军是一位排名较后的选手.

sentences.en: This qualifier means there must be at least m repetitions , and at most n.
sentences.cn: 该限定符的意思是至少有m个重复, 至多到n个重复.
